<Plugin>
  <Name>Dynamix File Recycle Bin</Name>
  <Overview>Adds a guarded recycle action and validated per-volume allowlist to Dynamix File Manager for verified internal /mnt/diskN volumes and local ZFS datasets. Each enabled disk or dataset owns its persistent .RecycleBin and SQLite history.</Overview>
